#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:152
msgid ""
"When enabled, other users can see when you are active. This feature is not "
"yet available."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diaktifkan, pengguna lain dapat melihat kapan Anda aktif. Fitur ini "
"belum tersedia."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:90
msgid ""
"When enabled, synchronizes your user data, Spaces, and Space keys between "
"devices. Enabling this increases metadata visibility of your account, which "
"can reveal when you have joined new Spaces, although not the Spaces you have"
" joined."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diaktifkan, menyinkronkan data pengguna Anda, Spaces, dan kunci Space"
" antara perangkat. Mengaktifkan ini meningkatkan visibilitas metadata "
"akunmu, yang dapat mengungkapkan kapan Anda telah bergabung dengan Spaces "
"baru, meskipun bukan Spaces yang telah Anda ikuti."

#: src/components/modals/SpaceSettingsModal/General.tsx:281
msgid ""
"When messages are signed, senders confirm they come from their key. When "
"messages aren't signed, senders have plausible deniability. This setting "
"applies to all messages in this Space."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pesan ditandatangani, pengirim mengonfirmasi bahwa pesan tersebut "
"berasal dari kunci mereka. Ketika pesan tidak ditandatangani, pengirim "
"memiliki alasan yang dapat diterima. Pengaturan ini berlaku untuk semua "
"pesan di Space ini."

#: src/components/modals/ConversationSettingsModal.tsx:244
msgid ""
"When muted, new messages won't show unread indicators or desktop "
"notifications."
msgstr ""
"Saat dibisukan, pesan baru tidak akan menampilkan indikator tidak terbaca "
"atau notifikasi desktop."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:132
msgid ""
"When on, anyone with your Quorum address can see your display name, avatar, "
"and bio, even outside the Spaces you share. Useful when someone DMs you and "
"you want them to recognize who you are. Off by default."
msgstr ""
"Saat diaktifkan, siapa pun dengan alamat Quorum Anda dapat melihat nama "
"tampilan, avatar, dan bio Anda, bahkan di luar Space yang Anda bagikan. "
"Berguna saat seseorang mengirim DM kepada Anda dan Anda ingin mereka "
"mengenali siapa Anda. Nonaktif secara default."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:250
msgid ""
"When on, everyone in a Space channel sees when you're typing, and you see "
"when they're typing."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, semua orang di kanal Space melihat saat Anda mengetik, dan Anda "
"melihat saat mereka mengetik."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:179
msgid ""
"When on, senders see when their messages reach your device, and you see when"
" yours reach theirs."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, pengirim melihat kapan pesan mereka sampai ke perangkat Anda, "
"dan Anda melihat kapan pesan Anda sampai ke perangkat mereka."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:203
msgid ""
"When on, senders see when you've read their messages, and you see when yours"
" are read."
msgstr ""
"Saat aktif, pengirim melihat kapan Anda telah membaca pesan mereka, dan Anda"
" melihat kapan pesan Anda telah dibaca."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:273
msgid ""
"When on, your device fetches thumbnails from YouTube for the links you send,"
" which reveals your IP to Google. When off, recipients see a plain link "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diaktifkan, perangkat Anda mengambil thumbnail dari YouTube untuk "
"tautan yang Anda kirim, yang mengungkapkan IP Anda ke Google. Ketika "
"dimatikan, penerima melihat tautan biasa saja."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:227
msgid ""
"When on, your DM contacts see when you're typing, and you see when they're "
"typing."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diaktifkan, kontak DM Anda melihat kapan Anda sedang mengetik, dan "
"Anda melihat kapan mereka sedang mengetik."

